<ITEM>Jo&s;eph Wood,</ITEM>
<ITEM>William Biles,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Jo&s;eph Growdon,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Tobias Dymmoke,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Richard Hough,</ITEM>
<ITEM>William Paxton,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Jeremiah Langhorn,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Jo&s;hua Hoopes,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Thomas Steven&s;on,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Rowland Ellis,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Nicholas Walne,</ITEM>
<ITEM>Samuel Richard&s;on,</ITEM>
<ITEM>I&s;aac Norris,</ITEM>
<ITEM>David Lloyd, <HI>Speaker,</HI></ITEM>
